      "writtenOn": "2020-09-18T17:22:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "TBH, i don\u0027t see why this is useful. 3 string parameters especially are harder to get right than naming fields like L91..L99.\n\nAlso, writes should always be in a transacton:\n read existing (if any)\n validate the write is still necessary\n write",
      "range": {
