      "writtenOn": "2020-09-18T17:22:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This creates doubles RAM usage. For \u003c1 MiB, doesn\u0027t matter, but then splitting into Groups isn\u0027t useful anyhow.\nFor large configs, however, we should be careful. I think ideal approach would avoid copying proto and copy pb.ConfigGroup by reference just ahead of ds.Put(),\nand because of DS limits, we should .Put() them sequentially.\n\nhence, i\u0027d instead do `writeConfigGroups`",
